General.Name: Excellerant Inc
General.Description: Excellerant, Inc., a development stage company, focuses on providing a range of health advisory and tour services to legal entities and individuals. The company intends to offer consulting services in the field of traditional and alternative medicine, and medical technologies; for customers to choose a clinic for treatment, as well as arrange the itinerary by building a route, which includes clinics, hospitals, and other medical institutions; and providing guide services to potential clients. Further, it provides information related to transportation and medical institutions. The company was incorporated in 2019 and is based in Brussels, Belgium. Excellerant, Inc. is a subsidiary of Swamson Capital AG.
